# SecuredDNS

SecuredDNS is a lightweight, standards-compliant DNS resolver with enhanced security features.  
It implements DNS over TLS (DoT) and DNSSEC validation to protect against spoofing and interception.

---

## âœ¨ Features
- DNS over TLS (DoT) support using OpenSSL
- DNSSEC validation for authenticity
- Configurable upstream resolvers (default: Cloudflare 1.1.1.1)
- Cross-platform C implementation
- BSD-licensed for open-source use

